PersonalName - Class in edu.odu.cs.cs350.namex
The personal name class stores a personal name as an arraylist The prefix (IE: Mr, Dr, Mrs, Governor, Senator, Professor)will be stored in the first index of the arraylist The suffix (IE: Jr, Sr, III) will be stored as the second index of the arraylist The given name will be stored in the third index The surname will be stored in the final index Any middle names will be stored between the 3rd and final indices.
